{"tid":2154063,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"見到個陣扯撚晒旗咁","createTime":"2020-08-13T02:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T09:45:42.000Z","uid":338435,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5c14a0175f05fc6510e600910bae63ff2c314e8a","tid":2154063,"uid":338435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jafE9GF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjafE9GF.jpg&h=79a692a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DWBduGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDWBduGF.jpg&h=0066dab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n心諗係咪可以免費讀degree <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a06799f4940638da29340d821e8191a2d31bfa","tid":2154063,"uid":15195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:20:45.000Z","msg":"安祥地去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a174a69952418f9ffde756b0871191f1c4707b","tid":2154063,"uid":338435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:20:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd3bbd452167e5d836fff06690f66a19448f7df","tid":2154063,"uid":112390,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:20:51.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\nnonju有自己嘅難處同彩數 <br />\n<br />\n如有得揀dse直入 邊個唔想<br />\n我都有努力過 我都試過每日訓4個鐘咁去溫書 操pp<br />\n咁我唔得即係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人鍾意男人 有人鍾意女人<br />\n各有取向<br />\n<br />\n有人適合DSE高壓模式一試定生死<br />\n有人適合HD/Asso持續考核GPA計分<br />\n各有自己選擇<br />\n<br />\n啲人覺得DSE考得差就一定係讀唔到書？一定唔應該入大學？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就真係勸啲人睇多啲書 唔好坐井觀天、活在自己嘅世界<br />\n<br />\n同埋nonju入hku唔令我覺得羞恥 亦唔係後門狗 nonju入hku係光明正大寫喺hku個website<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係啲人覺得只有DSE jupas先係光明正大入HKU嘅唯一選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lmao  <br />\n<br />\nnonju都用自己努力考gpa 一步一步升上去 <br />\n（定係你覺得讀嘅hd/asso畀完錢就乜都唔洗理gpa自己就會好似啲警察受武肺感染人數咁自動升升升）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係畀錢 唔係靠關係 光明正大咁用非DSE嘅方式入HKU 我就真係唔知啲人憑乜嘢講nonju係走後門<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實對比返我自己讀中學嘅經驗<br />\n讀完hd/asso嘅人 比起freshgrade嘅中學生<br />\n某程度上佢哋有更多嘅經驗喺接受全英嘅教學、寫paper &amp;reference （apa format）、group work合作、使用learn portal、應對freerider、睇百幾頁嘅ppt etc.（有錯望諒）<br />\n<br />\n大家雖然起點唔一樣 但最終都係為左讀大學 增長自己知識和技能 更好地融如社會 <br />\n未步入社會工作就已經要開始批鬥 分門別類 去區分前門後門 真係值得驕傲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而至於hall收唔收我 唔到我話 <br />\n咁我禮拜一就打去admission office問下nonju嘅學生入唔入到hku 嘅hall<br />\n<br />\n而你用你認知嘅HKU hall文化覺得佢哋未必收我<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">抑或可能係你<strong>坐井觀天</strong>呢？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後同宜家讀緊hd/asso嘅人講聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝你來年過3爆4入到U"},{"pid":"9e41706ca1b220c3905062b78898fedcc0c302ee","tid":2154063,"uid":338435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:22:05.000Z","msg":"之前以為珠海學院喺係珠海讀 原來屯門就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a241fc84a73b19c7c7502d4e457bd427564ee4d","tid":2154063,"uid":338435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"有免費degree呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c6769a06e3376a4a256b63d460b4c3a26fa1d7","tid":2154063,"uid":302151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a241fc84a73b19c7c7502d4e457bd427564ee4d","tid":2154063,"uid":338435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"有免費degree呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:32:45.000Z","msg":"讀左等於冇讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9ad7a8dd9a23e8df5dbdd05fc39faf162bf224","tid":2154063,"uid":338435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8c6769a06e3376a4a256b63d460b4c3a26fa1d7","tid":2154063,"uid":302151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a241fc84a73b19c7c7502d4e457bd427564ee4d","tid":2154063,"uid":338435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"有免費degree呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:32:45.000Z","msg":"讀左等於冇讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:33:18.000Z","msg":"Degree喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"